: Escalate Privileges in AWS Using EC2 Instance Roles
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Identify EC2 instance roles with excessive IAM permissions
Exploit misconfigured EC2 roles to escalate privileges in AWS environments
Automate privilege escalation detection using Python and AWS SDK
Implement defensive measures to prevent EC2 role-based privilege escalation
Recognize common IAM misconfigurations that enable privilege escalation
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of AWS IAM, EC2, and STS services
Familiarity with Linux command line operations
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of JSON format and AWS policy documents
